data.description: RECENTLY REMODELED! Updated photos coming this weekend!LOOKING FOR A FARM!!! We've got the perfect property for you! Completely setup for your animals, city water, electric, and amazing 360 degree views. This slice of paradise is only 15 mins from I-10, Palm Desert, Bermuda Dunes or Rancho Mirage, 10 min to DHS, 20 min to Palm Springs Airport. Quiet and secluded this 3 bed 2 bath home has been updated and renovated to give you high quality windows and doors, modern mini split A/C system. The Chefs kitchen features beautiful finished wood counters, shaker cabinets and farm sink. Stainless appliances and walk-in pantry make this kitchen ready for your next meal. Check out the updated bathrooms, comfortable and spacious, they were recently updated to the modern trends and expense was not spared. Outside you will find solace on your 2.63 acres of land. 3 separate animal enclosures, running water around the property, ready for you and your animals. The best getaway is the one you come home to everyday. Sellers are motivated, come see this property today! CITY WATER! IID For Electric! House was painted after photos to be a much nicer color. SELLERS ARE OFFERING A CLOSING COST CREDIT!
